    <thetext>The synfig spec file says:

%configure --disable-static --with-imagemagick --with-magickpp \
        --without-libavcodec
        CPPFLAGS=&apos;-DMagickLib=MagickCore -I/usr/include/ImageMagick&apos;

The CPPFLAGS variable will not be passed to configure, because there is a missing backslash on the line before it, and CPPFLAGS is not one of the variables exported by %configure

Presumably the line doesn&apos;t do anything and so could be removed, but someone who knows this package should determine that and decide what to do.</thetext>
